# 1. Ignore all data directories (prevents pushing raw data)
**/data/

# 2. Ignore all submission directories (prevents pushing heavy submission CSVs)
**/submissions/

# 3. Blanket rule: Ignore all CSV and ZIP files anywhere in the project
*.csv
*.zip

# 4. Ignore CatBoost/LightGBM training log folders
catboost_info/
